text: Nóra Varsányi (born 3 October 1991 in Debrecen) is a retired Hungarian handballer who played for Debreceni VSC in right wing position until 2020. ==Achievements== *Nemzeti Bajnokság I: **Silver Medallist: 2011 ==References== ==External links== * Nóra Varsányi player profile on Debreceni VSC Official Website * Nóra Varsányi career statistics at Worldhandball Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Debrecen Category:Hungarian female handball players
